class="awb-icon-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-8 fusion_builder_column_1_2 1_2 fusion-flex-column fusion-flex-align-self-flex-start" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:50%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:60px;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:60px;--awb-width-medium:50%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:60px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:60px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:60px;--awb-margin-bottom-small:90px;--awb-spacing-left-small:60px;" data-scroll-devices="small-visibility,medium-visibility,large-visibility"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-4 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two" style="--awb-margin-bottom:0px;--awb-font-size:25px;"><h2 class="fusion-title-heading title-heading-left" style="margin:0;font-size:1em;line-height:30px;"><p style="text-align: justify;">Our Infrastructure &amp; Handcrafted Mastery</p></h2></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-title-5 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-six" style="--awb-margin-bottom:0px;"><h6 class="fusion-title-heading title-heading-left" style="font-family:&quot;Quattrocento Sans&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0;line-height:30px;"><p style="text-align: justify;">Have worked with more than <strong>400+ designers &amp; brands</strong> across <strong>30 countries</strong> and have been consistently recognised for exceptional quality &amp; on-time delivery.</p></h6></div><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-builder-row-inner fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap" style="width:calc( 100% + 120px ) !important;max-width:calc( 100% + 120px ) !important;margin-left: calc(-120px / 2 );margin-right: calc(-120px / 2 );"><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column_inner fusion-builder-nested-column-0 fusion_builder_column_inner_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:-5px;--awb-spacing-right-large:60px;--awb-margin-bottom-large:15px;--awb-spacing-left-large:60px;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:60px;--awb-spacing-left-medium:60px;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:60px;--awb-spacing-left-small:60px;" data-scroll-devices="small-visibility,medium-visibility,large-visibility"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><ul style="--awb-item-padding-top:0.7em;--awb-item-padding-bottom:0.7em;--awb-iconcolor:#aa7247;--awb-line-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-width:27.2px;--awb-icon-height:27.2px;--awb-icon-margin:11.2px;--awb-content-margin:38.4px;--awb-circlecolor:var(--awb-color2);--awb-circle-yes-font-size:14.08px;" class="fusion-checklist fusion-checklist-1 fusion-checklist-divider type-icons"><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>State-of-the-art German Casting Plant &amp; Machinery</strong></div></li><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>Team of 850+ skilled craftsmen &amp; 100+ quality assurance experts.</strong></div></li><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>A dedicated team of 40+ Experienced CAD professionals</strong></div></li><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>Engineered for a daily output of 6,000+ jewelry pieces.</strong></div></li><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>State-of-the-art German laser soldering &amp; marking machines.</strong></div></li><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>Equipped with German plating machinery &amp; advanced German XRF Machine.</strong></div></li><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>Utilizing premium German &amp; Swiss plating Solutions for exceptional quality.</strong></div></li><li class="fusion-li-item" style=""><span class="icon-wrapper circle-yes"><i class="fusion-li-icon fa-chevron-circle-right fas" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><div class="fusion-li-item-content"><strong>Extensive in-house gemstone manufacturing offering over 200+ natural &amp; lab-grown gemstones.</strong></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div style="text-align:center;"><a class="fusion-button button-flat fusion-button-default-size button-custom fusion-button-default button-2 fusion-button-default-span fusion-button-default-type fusion-animated awb-b-icon-pos-left" style="--button_accent_color:#ffffff;--button_border_color:#dbc0b3;--button_accent_hover_color:var(--awb-color1);--button_border_hover_color:var(--awb-color3);--button_border_width-top:1px;--button_border_width-right:5px;--button_border_width-bottom:5px;--button_border_width-left:1px;--button_